.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, cooking, traveling, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
City: rome, new-york, venice, paris
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person traveling to rome and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
 5. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
 8. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
11. the person traveling to rome is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Hobby          | rock-climbing     | cooking | video-games | traveling  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| City           | venice | paris | rome    | new-york  |

