.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, roller, subway
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, mystery, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, purple, chestnut, light-blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 3. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 6. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
 7. the person who likes chestnut is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8
12. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Transport         | motorbike    | subway   | roller | quad-bike |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | mystery  | western   | drama      |
| Color   | purple | orange    | chestnut      | light-blue       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

