The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, may, august
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, light-blue, green, turquise
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person who likes lilac##6
 2. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person who likes green##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes light-blue##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
14. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
