 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person who growsmarigold##6
 8. the fan of soul is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
11. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
12. the fan of soul is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
13. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the fan of soul##8

