 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsiris##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person who growsbellflower##1
14. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
