10. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
11. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
12. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
