.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
4 different games are played: domino, poker, backgammon, snooker
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, woodworking, magic-tricks, baking
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
