 4. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person eating pepper##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the person eating corn##7
11. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
