.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, june, march
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, snowboarding, surfing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, reggae
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's birthday is in march##2
13. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday         | march    | june   | january   | august |
| Sport           | basketball | baseball    | snowboarding | surfing    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | jazz      | indie         | reggae     |

 